<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Katie Price has revealed that Harvey was 'chuffed with himself' on Monday after looking at a college as she shares a heartwarming picture of her eldest son. </p>

<p>The former glamour model, 42, posted a picture of a beaming Harvey Price, 18, to her Instagram and described how proud he was after visiting the further education centre.  </p>

<p>Harvey has multiple disabilities including blindness, Prader-Willi syndrome and ADHA and was rushed into intensive care in June experiencing extreme chest pains.  </p>

<p>Proud: Katie Price,  42, has revealed that Harvey was 'chuffed with himself' on Monday after looking at a college as she shares a heartwarming picture of her eldest son</p>

<p>'Chuffed': The mother-of-five shared a picture of Harvey smiling in the back of a car, captioned: 'Harvey <?php echo e('@'); ?>officialmrharveyprice chuffed with himself today as he looked at a college and looking trendy in his <?php echo e('@'); ?>bigclothing4u_ fashionable clothes'</p>

<p>The mother-of-five shared a picture of Harvey smiling in the back of a car, captioned: 'Harvey <?php echo e('@'); ?>officialmrharveyprice chuffed with himself today as he looked at a college and looking trendy in his <?php echo e('@'); ?>bigclothing4u_ fashionable clothes.' </p>

<p>The post garnered more than 12,547 likes and well-wishers described how they were overjoyed for Harvey. </p>

<p>One wrote: 'Such a talented boy so proud of him and you're a brilliant mum he is a credit to you.' </p>

<p>Support: Harvey has multiple disabilities including blindness, Prader-Willi syndrome and ADHA and was rushed into intensive care in June experiencing extreme chest pains (pictured in July) </p>

<p>Another penned: 'Aww he should be chuffed with himself. Enjoy your new college.' </p>

<p>A third added: 'Well done Harvey - wish you the best.'  </p>

<p>Earlier this month, Katie revealed Harvey, who does not have a relationship with his biological father, Dwight Yorke, wanted her boyfriend Carl Woods to be his dad.</p>

<p>In an Instagram video, Katie asked: 'Harv, what do you want mummy and Carl to do?' to which the teenager responded: 'Be with mummy and Harvey and Carl... your daddy.'  </p>

<p>Katie confirmed: 'You want Carl to be your what?' as her son responded, 'Harvey's daddy.'</p>

<p>Well-wishes: The post garnered more than 12,547 likes and well-wishes described how they were overjoyed for Harvey</p>

<p>As Katie asked Harvey: 'Do you? Do you love Carl that much?' he replied, 'Yes mum.'</p>

<p>As she added, 'You're so cute', Harvey went, 'I know, tell me about it.'   </p>

<p>Katie dated Harvey's biological father Dwight, 48, from 2000-2001, and has criticised the footballer for his alleged lack of contact with Harvey. </p>

<p>In her 2016 book Reborn, the mother-of-five insisted Dwight was unwilling to accept the limitations of his son's disabilities. </p>

<p>Son: Harvey, who has multiple disabilities including blindness, Prader-Willi syndrome and ADHA, does not have a relationship with his biological father, Dwight Yorke</p>

<p>In June Harvey was rushed to intensive care after he had trouble breathing. </p>

<p>He experienced extreme chest-pains and a soaring temperature and was thought to be at risk of organ failure. </p>

<p>Katie recalled seeing eight doctors crowding around him in the resuscitation room and said she was 'terrified' by the horrific ordeal.</p>

<p>Harvey was discharged from hospital in July ten days after he was rushed into intensive care.  </p>

<p>Due to Harvey's complex needs, he lives in residential care, but has been home with Katie amid the coronavirus pandemic. </p>

<p>Katie is also mother to son Junior, 15, and daughter Princess, 13, with ex-husband Peter Andre and son Jett, six, and daughter Bunny, five, with estranged husband Kieran Hayler. </p>

<p>Estranged: Katie shares Harvey with ex Dwight Yorke, they had split by the time she gave birth. The model has since criticised the sportsman for his treatment of their son</p>
